sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler
    participant Advisory
    participant Weather
    participant Irrigation

    Scheduler->>Advisory: Trigger irrigation evaluation
    Advisory->>Weather: Fetch forecast & rain history
    Weather-->>Advisory: Weather data

    Advisory->>Advisory: Evaluate irrigation rules

    Advisory->>Advisory: Wait for cancellation window

    Advisory->>Irrigation: Start irrigation
    Irrigation-->>Advisory: IrrigationCompleted
